list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Completely reworked my scss file structure. Moved most of my files into a few folders and broke them apart into smaller files. This change was inpsired from changes I was making to nearly every project I worked on. The current structure had too many classes that could fit into one or more files, so this helps differentiate which classes should be in which files.

task.summary: Updated a lot of the SASS to include some classes that I use in a lot of designs.
Contact.php was living in the wrong spot, so I moved it to its correct folder.
